        <div class="cm-h1 w3-large">
          The goal of this item was to showcase that while the techniques of additive manufacturing seem very technical, they can still be used in an artistic application.
        </div>
        <div class="w3-row w3-center">
          <div class="w3-quarter">
            <img class="w3-image" src="/static/shadow_orb/projection.jpg" alt="" style="max-height:400px;">
